title: Dr Katz MP3
description:
Video is nice and all, but here&#039;s something to help you wet your pants on the way to work. Since Dr. Katz is essentially stand-up comedy, audio only does the job. It easily fits on two MP3 CDs and includes the guide website to help you know what&#039;s what. Be kind, and seed at least equal to what you download.

Also, DivX is coming -- but having a lot of sync problems.
